OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,FMagilligan has been described as one
OL,7,Fof the best prisons in the UK in an
OL,8,Finspection report that praised its
OL,9,F"excellent" staff-prisoner
OL,10,Frelationships.
OL,12,FAn unannounced inspection was carried
OL,13,Fout into the prison near Limavady in
OL,14,FSeptember, by Criminal Justice
OL,15,FInspection Northern Ireland (CJI), and
OL,16,Finspectors from three other
OL,17,Forganisations.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,FThey found good staff-prisoner
OL,7,Frelationships and lower levels of
OL,8,Fviolence and use of force than in
OL,9,Fsimilar prions in England and Wales.
OL,11,FChief inspector of CJI Jacqui Durkin,
OL,12,Fand chief inspector of HM's
OL,13,FInspectorate of Prisons in England and
OL,14,FWales, Charlie Taylor, said it was
OL,15,Fconsidered one of the best prisons in
OL,16,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,F"Outcomes for the men held at
OL,7,FMagilligan Prison had improved since
OL,8,Four last inspection in 2021 and were
OL,9,Fassessed as 'good' against each of the
OL,10,Ffour healthy prison tests of safety,
OL,11,Frespect, purposeful activity and
OL,12,Fpreparation for release," they said.
OL,14,FWhile the report noted some areas of
OL,15,Fconcern, it added: "Magilligan,
OL,16,Fhowever, is now one of the very best
OL,17,Fprisons in the United Kingdom, and
OL,18,Fleaders and staff can rightly be proud
OL,19,Fof the positive, rehabilitative
OL,20,Fenvironment they have created."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@YO]wD@TOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,FThe report raised four priority and
OL,7,Fseven key concerns, including in
OL,8,Frelation to drug use at the prison,
OL,9,Fwith almost a quarter of prisoners
OL,10,Fsaying they had developed a problem
OL,11,Fwith drug misuse while at the prison.
OL,13,F"The misuse of drugs by prisoners,
OL,14,Fincluding prescription medication,
OL,15,Firrespective of who prescribed it or
OL,16,Fhow it has got into the possession of
OL,17,Fa prisoner who should not be taking
OL,18,Fit, is a threat to the prison's
OL,19,Fstability," said Ms Durkin.
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,F"While we acknowledge the steps being
OL,7,Ftaken to prevent drugs entering the
OL,8,Fprison, inadequate funding and lengthy
OL,9,Fwaiting lists for substance misuse and
OL,10,Faddiction services is contributing to
OL,11,Fthe likelihood of prisoners resorting
OL,12,Fto illegitimate drug use to manage
OL,13,Ftheir addictions within the prison."
OL,15,FConcerns were also raised about
OL,16,Finfrastructure, such as the Second
OL,17,FWord War Nissen huts that are used to
OL,18,Fhost workshops.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,FInspectors found 19 examples of
OL,7,Fnotable positive practice, that other
OL,8,Fprisons could learn from or adopt, and
OL,9,Fthat 22 of the 30 recommendations made
OL,10,Fafter the last inspection had been
OL,11,Fachieved in full or in part.
OL,13,FThe Education and Training
OL,14,FInspectorate found the education
OL,15,Fprovision for prisoners to be
OL,16,Fgenerally of good quality and the
OL,17,Flevel of attainment had improved, with
OL,18,F43% of qualifications achieved at
OL,19,FLevel 2.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,FInspectors also found evidence of good
OL,7,Fsupport and the use of mentors to help
OL,8,Fprisoners with literacy.
OL,10,FMr Taylor noted that time out of cell
OL,11,Fwas also found to be among the best
OL,12,Finspectors had seen in recent years,
OL,13,Fwith prisoners unlocked for between
OL,14,Feight to 10 hours each day, and only a
OL,15,Ffew prisoners not involved in
OL,16,Feducation, skills, work or other
OL,17,Factivities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,FDevelopments in healthcare were also
OL,7,Fhighlighted, including the appointment
OL,8,Fof a learning and disability nurse to
OL,9,Fwork with neurodivergent prisoners and
OL,10,Fthose with learning disabilities.
OL,12,FIt also praised a formal data-sharing
OL,13,Fagreement between the prison and the
OL,14,FSouth Eastern Health and Social Care
OL,15,FTrust, representing the first
OL,16,Felectronic shared record of its kind
OL,17,Fand considered a leading example
OL,18,Facross the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,FMs Durkin also noted that prisoners
OL,7,Fwere supported with maintaining family
OL,8,Fties and friendships and said 72% of
OL,9,Fprisoners said their experiences at
OL,10,FMagilligan had made them less likely
OL,11,Fto reoffend.
OL,13,F"Staff knew the men in their care and
OL,14,Fwere able to offer bespoke support to
OL,15,Findividual prisoners," Ms Durkin said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,F"These positive relationships
OL,7,Funderpinned much of the good work the
OL,8,Finspection team saw and contributed to
OL,9,Fthe low level of violence and use of
OL,10,Fforce compared to other similar
OL,11,Fprisons in England and Wales."
OL,13,FGovernor of Magilligan Gary Milling
OL,14,Fpaid tribute to everyone working in
OL,15,Fthe prison, and said it was the
OL,16,Fculmination of many years of hard work.
OL,18,F"We like to think of Magilligan as a
OL,19,Ffamily, made up of many parts," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@^O]zD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,F"Firstly, the leadership team and
OL,7,Fprison staff, but also the many
OL,8,Fpartner agencies that work so hard to
OL,9,Fmake this prison a success.
OL,11,F"While there are too many to name,
OL,12,Feach of them is a vital part in our
OL,13,Fwork to support and challenge the men
OL,14,Fin our care, and to play our part in
OL,15,Fbuilding a safer Northern Ireland."
OL,17,FJustice Minister Naomi Long welcomed
OL,18,Fthe inspection report and said it was
OL,19,Fan "outstanding result" for Magilligan
OL,20,FPrison.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@cO]{D@DOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,F"To be recognised as one of the best
OL,7,Fprisons in the UK is a significant
OL,8,Fachievement, particularly when our
OL,9,Fentire justice system is operating
OL,10,Funder such immense pressure.
OL,12,F"What stands out most in this report
OL,13,Fis the culture of respect. Our prisons
OL,14,Fare at their most effective when they
OL,15,Ffocus on rehabilitation and hope.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,F"By providing a safe and supportive
OL,7,Fenvironment, Magilligan is not just
OL,8,Fholding people in custody; it is
OL,9,Factively reducing the likelihood of
OL,10,Freoffending and making our entire
OL,11,Fcommunity safer.
OL,13,F"I want to thank the governor, Gary
OL,14,FMilling, and his staff for their
OL,15,Fcommitment to excellence."
OL,17,FBeverley Wall, director general of the
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland Prison Service, said
OL,19,FMagilligan being described "as a model
OL,20,Ffor the rest of the UK is a
OL,21,Fsignificant achievement".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@ZO]{D@\OU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774490589
OL,3,CMagilligan praised as one of the best
OL,4,CUK prisons in inspection report
OL,6,FShe added: "I am extremely proud of
OL,7,Fthe team at Magilligan. This
OL,8,Finspection report validates what we
OL,9,Fhave long recognised, that the
OL,10,Fleadership and staff at this
OL,11,Festablishment are delivering to an
OL,12,Fexceptionally high standard."
OL,26,@nD@LOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
